      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm a high school debate coach and I'm prepping my kids for a tournament next week. One of our rounds is on immigration policy. Can you help me out by steelmanning the strongest possible arguments for increased border security and much stricter immigration enforcement? I want my students to have the most robust version of that position so they know exactly what they're up against during rebuttals.",
