      "content": "Increased border security and stricter immigration enforcement are essential to maintaining the sovereignty and safety of our nation. Stronger borders protect our economy by ensuring that only those who meet our rigorous standards can enter, thus preserving jobs and resources for our citizens. Additionally, stricter enforcement prevents illegal activities such as human trafficking and drug smuggling, ensuring that our communities remain safe and secure. By prioritizing our national security and economic stability, we can create a more prosperous and orderly society.",
